snippet.title: Super Adventure Pals Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for Super Adventure Pals
A lovable action RPG spanning 75 levels, 4 boss fights, 3 towns (across 3 themed areas), countless interactive NPCs, experience based levelling up as well as special upgrades only available by replaying levels!
A game by Corupt3d and JayArmstrongGames

corupt3d : corupted.com
JayArmstrongGames : jayarmstronggames.com
